Package PatrolAllocation

package PatrolAllocation
This package represents the Patrol Allocation problem.

This package is used to determine solutions to the Patrol Allocation problem. It evaluates of each solution and prints the simulation results.

  • Class
    Description
    IndividualSolution
    Class that represents an individual solution for patrol allocation.
    PatrolAllocation
    Class that handles the initialization and setup of the patrol allocation problem.
    PatrolAllocationFactory
    Factory class to initialize the PatrolAllocation components.
    PrintCurrentResults
    Interface for printing current results of the patrol allocation simulation.
    ResultsPrinter
    Class responsible for printing the current results of the patrol allocation simulation.
